                     <interp inst="t18370130-683-punishment-167" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def2-683-18370130 t18370130-683-punishment-167"></join>Transported for Seven Years</rs>.</p>
               <p>(There was another indictment against Fishington, for stealing ten hats.)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Recorder</hi>.</p>
